    <svcsubsec>
        <title>COMPONENT LOCATIONS</title>
        <svcsubsecinfo>
            <para>This section provides the location of the components for removal and installation of the air
                conditioning protection and diagnostics system (APADS) in the 4000, 8000, 9100, 9200, 9300, 9400, 9800,
                and 9900 series vehicles.
            </para>
        </svcsubsecinfo>
